   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "290.480", 
   "id": "s000093", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einen solchen Vorschlag und eine solch unsoziale Mietpolitik lehnen wir grunds\u00e4tzlich ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "290.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "291.960", 
   "id": "s000094", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen wir einmal nach, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "291.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.160", 
   "id": "s000095", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es in den Bundesl\u00e4ndern aussieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.800", 
   "id": "s000096", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen die Linkspartei Regierungsverantwortung tr\u00e4gt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.800", 
   "id": "s000097", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Th\u00fcringen stellen Sie den Ministerpr\u00e4sidenten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.720", 
   "id": "s000098", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Landtagswahlkampf hatte dieser gute Mann die Wiedereinf\u00fchrung der Verm\u00f6gensteuer nicht nur gefordert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "308.800", 
   "id": "s000099", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch angek\u00fcndigt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "308.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.200", 
   "id": "s000100", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er sagte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.240", 
   "id": "s000101", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn er Ministerpr\u00e4sident werde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "310.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.120", 
   "id": "s000102", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werde er \u00fcber den Bundesrat ein entsprechendes Gesetzgebungsverfahren in Gang bringen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "318.720", 
   "id": "s000103", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als Rot-Rot-Gr\u00fcn den Koalitionsvertrag geschmiedet hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "318.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.200", 
   "id": "s000104", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "war noch von einer Verm\u00f6gensteuerinitiative im Bundesrat die Rede."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "324.440", 
   "id": "s000105", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schauen wir uns an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "324.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "326.280", 
   "id": "s000106", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es vier Jahre sp\u00e4ter aussieht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "326.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.640", 
   "id": "s000107", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nichts ist passiert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "327.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "332.920", 
   "id": "s000108", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt keinen Gesetzentwurf des Bundesrats zur Wiedereinf\u00fchrung der Verm\u00f6gensteuer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "332.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "334.280", 
   "id": "s000109", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "334.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "337.880", 
   "id": "s000110", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anscheinend ist man in der Regierungsverantwortung kl\u00fcger geworden.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "337.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "342.080", 
   "id": "s000111", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Erkenntnisgewinn fehlt der Linksfraktion noch. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "342.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "344.560", 
   "id": "s000112", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt haben wir vier Jahre Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "344.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "346.560", 
   "id": "s000113", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier vielleicht nachzuhelfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "346.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "351.240", 
   "id": "s000114", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir lehnen auf jeden Fall eine solche unsoziale Politik f\u00fcr die Mieter, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "351.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "355.720", 
   "id": "s000115", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr die Familienunternehmen und f\u00fcr die Arbeitspl\u00e4tze in Deutschland ab."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "355.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "356.800", 
   "id": "s000116", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "356.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "360.960", 
   "id": "s000117", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
